# Globals CSS Color Contrast Tokens

When editing color tokens in `src/app/globals.css`:

- Dark mode (`:root`) `--primary-foreground` must always be `#ffffff` (never `#020617`).
- Light mode `--text-disabled` must be `#6b7280` or darker (never `#94a3b8`).
- Light mode `--text-muted` must be `#4b6080` or darker.
- All primary/danger buttons must have foreground color with contrast ratio >= `4.5:1`.
